Either open the project in Visual Studio 2015 or just run the game from /bin/Debug/SpaceHoovy.exe

Download: https://github.com/diggles/SpaceHoovy/blob/master/bin/Debug/SpaceHoovy.exe?raw=true

Avoid the knives by moving hoovy with your mouse

Not planning on any updates, just an afternoon project 

